<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Account Recovery - Ordo</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4B4B4B;
        background-color: #F5F5F5 !important;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        table-layout: fixed;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 15px;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 30px 25px;
        box-shadow: inset 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .logo {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #21209C;
    }
    .tagline {
        text-align: center;
        font-style: italic;
        color: #8A18A0;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 24px 56px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #21209C, #8A18A0);
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
   
/* Magas, keskeny, nagy térközű karakterek az OTP-hez */
.button.otp {
    font-family: "Arial Narrow", "Segoe UI", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 10px;        /* nagy térköz */
    line-height: 1;             /* kompakt sor */
    padding: 18px 36px;         /* nagyobb gombméret */
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
    transform: scaleY(1.12);    /* magasabb megjelenés */
    -webkit-transform: scaleY(1.12);
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

    .corner-decoration {
        width: 100%;
        height: 50px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #21209C, #8A18A0);
        border-radius: 0 0 50% 50%;
    }
    h2 {
        color: #2c2c2c;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    strong {
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <center class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="corner-decoration"></div>
            <br>
            <div class="logo">ORDO</div>
            <div class="tagline">Control Time. Protect Data.</div>
            
           <h2>Two-Step Verification Code</h2>
            <p>Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>We detected a login attempt to your <strong>Ordo</strong> account. To complete signing in, please use the code below:</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <span class="button otp" style="cursor: default;"><strong><%= otp %></strong></span>
            </p>
            <p>This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.</p>
            <p>If you did not attempt to sign in, please secure your account immediately and contact our <strong>support team</strong>.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Ordo Team</strong></p>
        
        </div>
    </center>
</body>
</html>
